snippet.title: Sticky Business – Official Pride Update Trailer | Games Baked in Germany Showcase
snippet.description:
Celebrate Pride Month with Sticky Business and explore the free Pride Update! Dive into the joy of managing your own cozy small business: designing stickers, fulfilling orders, and connecting with your customers' stories. Embrace the rainbow and express your creativity with 95 new stickers, 12 fresh goodies, and 2 glitter papers. Spread the love in your shop like never before!

Visit Steam and add Sticky Business to your wishlist now!: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2303350/Sticky_Business/
